{"tid":1418222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對於荃灣今日一事，我想表達小小嘢","createTime":"2019-08-05T18:07:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T19:34:20.000Z","uid":12184,"like":95,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"c92402c1ec53270f473e09c4057f17161170a11a","tid":1418222,"uid":12184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:07:56.000Z","msg":"今日都有發夢上前線，夢到個個傻閪黑社會比人打到咩咁，但有樣野我地必須要正視，特別係勇武手足，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好殺紅了眼</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">咁樣我地就會同d垃圾黑社會，警犬，藍絲無分別</span></strong></span>我地係要保護同伴，保護市民，而唔係見到一個比人打到就死，行過仲要個個掛住補一刀，而忘記左前線既手足<br />\n<br />\n我明白，我都好撚好撚憎佢地，但我地咁樣打左死人，我地就會步入失敗既開始，成個社會，特別d中間撚就會批評我地，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但都記住，對呢d人係唔洗手下留情，但打到一定程度時就用索帶索住佢算喇</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n所以我地記住永遠都要一條心<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化，不篤灰，不割蓆，齊上齊落be water</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n最後，多謝今日一齊發夢既荃灣手足同路人，我地成功守護左市民，避免左一次元朗般既悲劇，亦再次證實警黑合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c07cc50337a38e0e6af19ecb2d839322a83160a4","tid":1418222,"uid":26942,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:09:53.000Z","msg":"啱 打一下就夠 重擊膝 令佢即時無行動力 大力d 仲有後遺症"},{"pid":"22e645ea470dc8d41d33fd94961d0d5a92b458c0","tid":1418222,"uid":61002,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:10:18.000Z","msg":"咁又係，人類真係好化學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />特別係啲肥佬呀，廢老咁"},{"pid":"3f5e7837e0ebdce3b8fb3d6417682aa51dc51991","tid":1418222,"uid":12184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:12:04.000Z","msg":"幫手推比前線睇"},{"pid":"86f7e90d0253fdfaac091210e55a26a6f29997c2","tid":1418222,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:13:10.000Z","msg":"再推前少少, 我想講如果D狗冷處理定係唔夠警力, 會唔會轉場支援其他區?<br />\n好似荃灣咁, 搞足成日都係出左一次狗車, 不過最尾逼到佢出TIER14都係好事"},{"pid":"18d25d7efd347afa184cbe6a36409e354ec7319e","tid":1418222,"uid":151256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:13:40.000Z","msg":"真係唔好扑頭 (我知有和理非幫手叫<br />\n爆頭見血vs同身有傷 新聞張相出嚟效果好唔同"},{"pid":"24adf2d6ad01a9d84d1606a09a65f78f1030a77d","tid":1418222,"uid":272353,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:14:22.000Z","msg":"呢片睇落咁「暴力」，但條仆街即時有力氣企起身重舉中指，你就知巴絲們其實冇好用力⋯⋯"},{"pid":"11d256fe7677a6ef9f27d19bdeb336d71768d0b8","tid":1418222,"uid":254371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:15:16.000Z","msg":"捉就一定要捉<br />\n打就打十秒鐘<br />\n自己計時"},{"pid":"3cd8012338d03833f8f32cb49372a6d241423aa2","tid":1418222,"uid":12184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"86f7e90d0253fdfaac091210e55a26a6f29997c2","tid":1418222,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:13:10.000Z","msg":"再推前少少, 我想講如果D狗冷處理定係唔夠警力, 會唔會轉場支援其他區?<br />\n好似荃灣咁, 搞足成日都係出左一次狗車, 不過最尾逼到佢出TIER14都係好事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:15:20.000Z","msg":"會，今日荃灣手足發夢，去左葵芳，荔枝角，再番去荃灣，全程非常be water"},{"pid":"c6fbe83e10ed0b6bae227f68ae27f5b068cbd675","tid":1418222,"uid":187950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c92402c1ec53270f473e09c4057f17161170a11a","tid":1418222,"uid":12184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:07:56.000Z","msg":"今日都有發夢上前線，夢到個個傻閪黑社會比人打到咩咁，但有樣野我地必須要正視，特別係勇武手足，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好殺紅了眼</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">咁樣我地就會同d垃圾黑社會，警犬，藍絲無分別</span></s