y":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:47:11.000Z","msg":"我冇咁講呀，我只係覺得今日班義士完全正確<br />\n係無啦啦有人唔知咩居心話人殺紅了眼，又話人比仇恨支配"},{"pid":"f652bb01eb98f2966c23ea12df34cfa67339f48c","tid":1418222,"uid":240286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c92402c1ec53270f473e09c4057f17161170a11a","tid":1418222,"uid":12184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:07:56.000Z","msg":"今日都有發夢上前線，夢到個個傻閪黑社會比人打到咩咁，但有樣野我地必須要正視，特別係勇武手足，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好殺紅了眼</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">咁樣我地就會同d垃圾黑社會，警犬，藍絲無分別</span></strong></span>我地係要保護同伴，保護市民，而唔係見到一個比人打到就死，行過仲要個個掛住補一刀，而忘記左前線既手足<br />\n<br />\n我明白，我都好撚好撚憎佢地，但我地咁樣打左死人，我地就會步入失敗既開始，成個社會，特別d中間撚就會批評我地，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但都記住，對呢d人係唔洗手下留情，但打到一定程度時就用索帶索住佢算喇</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n所以我地記住永遠都要一條心<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化，不篤灰，不割蓆，齊上齊落be water</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n最後，多謝今日一齊發夢既荃灣手足同路人，我地成功守護左市民，避免左一次元朗般既悲劇，亦再次證實警黑合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:47:46.000Z","msg":"打緊時，你喺邊"},{"pid":"c0ca1e9ff9933188426d0da847f1173deaa65d13","tid":1418222,"uid":12184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22114b305ccf8f92d870befd2dda457b4f6207ba","tid":1418222,"uid":205566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d1ea25d7ff32ce7d4e98df82c57efdf09229db2","tid":1418222,"uid":12184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"319cba27f05dba4df47fbb34687c4666c4f4ef26","tid":1418222,"uid":2